DESIGNING MEANINGFUL ANIMATION - Val Head
	- animation have to have a purpose
	- the12principles.tumblr.com
	- timing and spacing: timing --> most important principle in animation
	- timing: duration
	- spacing: changing of speed
	- follow through: non tutto si ferma di botto
	- secondary action: azione secondaria che accompagna la primaria
	- similar objects animate in similar way: principio di somiglianza
	- entrata e uscita dallo stesso punto
	- artofthetitle.com
	- capptivate.co
	- uyi.io

